{"tid":809531,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"伊度奧曾當面怒斥賓尼迪斯：我只願為摩連奴踢翼鋒","createTime":"2018-09-07T09:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T13:12:11.000Z","uid":57237,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"89019c70b227eec4a15c57ff823525973e9f0604","tid":809531,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"近日，國米名宿史尼達在接受採訪時表示，賓尼迪斯曾要求伊度奧繼續在國米打左翼鋒，卻遭到拒絕。<br />\n　　2009-10賽季，摩連奴率領史尼達、米列圖和伊度奧為國米拿到了歐冠盃冠軍，在球隊當時的4231陣型中，伊度奧的位置是左翼鋒。<br />\n　　後來摩帥遠走班拿貝，賓尼迪斯上任後要求伊度奧繼續在國米打左翼鋒，史尼達回憶：「伊度奧為摩連奴打了左翼鋒，賓尼迪斯也這麼要求時，他說不，我只會為摩連奴那樣做（打翼鋒）。」<br />\n2010年12月底，國米官方宣佈與賓尼迪斯解約，當時距離他接過藍黑軍團教鞭剛剛半年時間，球隊在意甲17輪8勝5平4負，落後祖記2分排名第5。後來里安納度接手國米，率隊獲得意甲亞軍、意大利盃冠軍。<br />\n　　（肆客足球）"},{"pid":"f53193eedbd5820ebe8e7c29ef6bd769fc85eea4","tid":809531,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:35:01.000Z","msg":"公平咩"},{"pid":"3780812d005b72eaa25ef6c602f700b2aa7d0589","tid":809531,"uid":159523,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:38:13.000Z","msg":"暴聯新魔翼來了"},{"pid":"46ffd43a1d5a100a77218ad4b37cd8eef7f66024","tid":809531,"uid":42246,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:49:36.000Z","msg":"Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾時都話曼聯執到寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f7e185a17f0938dd0de8bdec0fabb35f15cd08","tid":809531,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T09:56:11.000Z","msg":"里安納度做戲勁 教波都咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4b301b7b12f7124a9fdebaf6d6d4a0668de39c","tid":809531,"uid":158499,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"29f7e